		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猎犬突然后撤，随后直接冲向玩家咬合，造成<span color="#ffe599">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猎犬后空翻消失，传送至玩家身后使用尾部击打造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每受到一次直接<span color="#ffe599">岩元素</span><span>伤害，其怒气值就增长20%，值满时猎犬的外观发生明显变化，永久</span><span color="#ffecbf">进入嗜魔状态</span><span>，以</span><span color="#ffc926">岩抗减至-40%</span><span>为代价提升攻击频率。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="432" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffebbf">(幼兽在场时施放)<span color="#ffffff">猎犬朝空中咆哮一下，赋予30m附近的任意幼兽</span><span color="#ffbfbf">25%的攻击力提升</span><span color="#ffffff">，持续10s，可叠加2层，每层持续时间独立计算。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">猎犬在近处进行左右两段划击攻击，两段攻击均造成<span color="#ffe599">85%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，猎犬使蓄力吐出一枚弱追踪岩晶，造成<span color="#ffe599">95%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffecbf">(嗜魔施放)<span color="#ffffff">猎犬后空翻朝玩家快速冲过来，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">85%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，持续3轮。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
